commit.message:
fix: ansi-inhibit-ansi must be applied during runtime

With ansi-inhibit-ansi the expansion of ansi-with was incorrect and
actually crashed execution.  Even with the inhibited ansi codes, we
must still walk the "DSL" tree and format the strings properly before
concatting them.
